OL,3,CLiverpool Football Club confirms
OL,4,Cpermanent tribute to honour Diogo Jota
OL,6,FLiverpool Football Club has
OL,7,Fcommissioned a sculpture to be made in
OL,8,Fhonour of Diogo Jota outside Anfield
OL,9,Fafter thousands of floral tributes to
OL,10,Ftheir No.20 were gradually removed in
OL,11,Frecent days.
OL,13,FPortugal and Liverpool forward Jota
OL,14,Fand his brother Andre Silva, who
OL,15,Fplayed for Portuguese second division
OL,16,Fclub Penafiel, died in a car crash on
OL,17,F3 July in the Spanish province of
OL,18,FZamora.
