OL,3,CLiverpool Football Club confirms
OL,4,Cpermanent tribute to honour Diogo Jota
OL,6,FLiverpool retired Jota's number 20
OL,7,Fshirt in tribute, across all levels of
OL,8,Fthe club, including LFC Women and the
OL,9,FAcademy.
OL,11,FThe planned sculpture will be made by
OL,12,Frecycling items left outside Anfield
OL,13,Fsince his death by fans paying their
OL,14,Frespects.
OL,16,FIt will become a permanent memorial
OL,17,Fsculpture that will become a future
OL,18,Ffocal point of remembrance at Anfield.
