OL,3,CLiverpool Football Club confirms
OL,4,Cpermanent tribute to honour Diogo Jota
OL,6,FFloral tributes are to be composted
OL,7,Fand used in flower beds across all
OL,8,Fclub sites, including Anfield, the AXA
OL,9,FTraining Centre and AXA Melwood
OL,10,FTraining Centre.
OL,12,FIn the meantime, a temporary area of
OL,13,Freflection has been created at Anfield
OL,14,Fso people can continue to pay their
OL,15,Frespects.
OL,17,FLiverpool are planning a fan mosaic
OL,18,Fand a minute's silence at the opening
OL,19,FPremier League home game against
OL,20,FBournemouth on 15 August.
