OL,3,CLiverpool Football Club confirms
OL,4,Cpermanent tribute to honour Diogo Jota
OL,6,FFans can also pay tribute at the pre-
OL,7,Fseason game against Atletico Bilbao on
OL,8,F4 August at Anfield, while players'
OL,9,Fshirts will have a "'Diogo J 20" patch
OL,10,Ffor their two pre-season games in Asia.
OL,12,FAnd the Reds players will wear a
OL,13,Fspecially-designed patch with 'Diogo J
OL,14,F20' stitched on in memory of their
OL,15,Fteam-mate across the two games in the
OL,16,FFar East, starting with AC Milan at
OL,17,Fthe Kai Tak Stadium on Saturday
OL,18,Fevening (12.30pm UK time).
