OL,3,CLiverpool Football Club confirms
OL,4,Cpermanent tribute to honour Diogo Jota
OL,6,FA floral tribute will also be laid
OL,7,Fbefore kick-off at the pre-season
OL,8,Fgames in Hong Kong, Tokyo and Anfield.
OL,10,FThe LFC Foundation has also committed
OL,11,Fto creating a grassroots football
OL,12,Fprogramme in the Jota's name.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, the Football Association
OL,15,Fwill hold talks with Liverpool before
OL,16,Fplanning a tribute to Jota at the
OL,17,FCommunity Shield at Wembley on 10
OL,18,FAugust.
