OL,3,CLiverpool Football Club confirms
OL,4,Cpermanent tribute to honour Diogo Jota
OL,6,FIn addition, the club have said if
OL,7,Fsupporters want to honour Jota by
OL,8,Fhaving "Diogo J 20" on the back of
OL,9,Ftheir shirts, then the profits of the
OL,10,Fpurchases will go to the LFC
OL,11,FFoundation, the club's charity.
OL,13,FLiverpool FC has expressed its
OL,14,Fheartfelt gratitude and appreciation
OL,15,Fto everyone who has taken the time,
OL,16,Fand continues to take the time, to
OL,17,Fleave tributes in honour of Diogo Jota
OL,18,Fand his brother Andre Silva at Anfield.
